Zsh - useful when working with your own machine.
Zsh is a shell that that takes all the goodness of all the others shell including bash and make it better. 
Esiest way to install zsh is by installing homebrew.
  - https://brew.sh
Just copy and paste the link in iTerm2 terminal.
Type the command brew install zsh in your Iterm2 Terminal
To make check it has been install run "echo $SHELL" if you see /bin/bash, bash is still running, 
to run zsh just type: chsh -s /bin/zsh + Enter, & confirm your password.




